item.title: Wilco here [Updated]
item.dc:creator: @lothy Lothy
item.description:
@lothy wrote:

[quote=“3lv3n snip3r, post:4, topic:531335”][quote author=Rodgerwilco link=topic=650098.msg4365689#msg4365689 date=1379632380]

are rares worth anything anymore?

Eh it has a little value but still a value. I think people are stuck on the runescape classic rares and forget that 07 has several different holiday events for each holiday. If I am right then it’s a long term investment… but still an investment. It’s a gamble that I am willing to put my money on. People say that rares are inflated and that’s how it was on rsc… I remember Christmas of 2001 there were like 50 party hats to each person and nobody cared for them.

I’ll cross my fingers.
[/quote]
Hopefully RS '07 will last long enough for that to happen.[/quote]
Wouldn’t count on it. The playerbase is only decreasing - no new players are likely to enter the game with a view to playing it seriously because, let’s face it, confidence in it being around in several months time is low.

Read full topic
